title: Virginia Tech shoots 53.8 percent from deep, defeats Syracuse 102-53 - VT hokiesports.com
content: Virginia Tech shoots 53.8 percent from deep, defeats Syracuse 102-53  VT hokiesports.com
description: SYRACUSE, NY --The Virginia Tech women's basketball team shot 53.8 percent from deep on the way to a 102-53 win against the Syracuse Orange on the road Thursday.
